# Lobby / Waiting Room + Host Controls for Meetify

Implement a production-ready waiting room (lobby) system where hosts control admission. When a meeting has `lobbyEnabled=true`, participants see a "Request to join" screen instead of directly entering. The host approves/denies requests in real-time via socket events. Also adds host controls (mute-all, remove, promote), page refresh confirmation, and premium UI.

## Architecture

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                         CLIENT (React)                               │
│                                                                      │
│  MeetingRoomPage                                                     │
│  ├── checks meeting.lobbyEnabled via REST                            │
│  ├── if lobby ON + not host → WaitingRoomView                        │
│  │   └── useLobby hook (join-request → wait → admitted/denied)       │
│  ├── if lobby OFF or host or admitted → MeetingRoom                  │
│  │   ├── useWebRTC hook (only after admit)                           │
│  │   ├── HostLobbyPanel (pending requests sidebar for host)          │
│  │   ├── JoinRequestToast (push notification)                        │
│  │   └── HostControlsPanel (mute-all, remove, promote, lock)        │
│  └── beforeunload handler for refresh confirmation                   │
│                                                                      │
│  Socket Events: join-request, join-request-cancel, request-accepted, │
│  request-denied, host-action, room-state, user-joined, etc.         │
└──────────────────┬───────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
                   │ socket.io / WebSocket
┌──────────────────▼───────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                       SERVER (NestJS)                                │
│                                                                      │
│  EventsGateway                                                       │
│  ├── rooms Map<roomId, RoomState> (existing)                         │
│  ├── pendingRequests Map<roomId, Map<socketId, JoinRequest>> (new)   │
│  ├── roomSettings Map<roomId, RoomSettings> (new)                    │
│  │                                                                   │
│  ├── handleJoinRoom → if lobbyEnabled, redirect to pending           │
│  ├── handleJoinRequest → create pending, notify host                 │
│  ├── handleApproveRequest → admit participant, emit room-state       │
│  ├── handleDenyRequest → notify participant                          │
│  ├── handleCancelRequest → remove pending, notify host               │
│  ├── handleHostAction → mute-all, remove, promote, lock             │
│  └── TTL cleanup interval (stale requests after N minutes)           │
│                                                                      │
│  Meeting Entity → +lobbyEnabled column                               │
│  MeetingsService → +update method (toggle lobby)                     │
│  MeetingsController → +PATCH endpoint                                │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

## Socket Event Contract

| Event | Direction | Payload |
|-------|-----------|---------|
| `join-request` | client→server | `{ roomId, userName, mediaState }` |
| `join-request-cancel` | client→server | `{ roomId }` |
| `join-request-received` | server→host | `{ socketId, userId, userName, mediaState, requestedAt }` |
| `join-request-cancelled` | server→host | `{ socketId }` |
| `approve-request` | host→server | `{ roomId, targetSocketId, role }` |
| `deny-request` | host→server | `{ roomId, targetSocketId, reason? }` |
| `bulk-approve` | host→server | `{ roomId, targets: [{socketId, role}] }` |
| `request-accepted` | server→participant | `{ role, roomState }` |
| `request-denied` | server→participant | `{ reason? }` |
| `host-action` | host→server | `{ roomId, action, targetSocketId?, ... }` |
| `host-action-applied` | server→room | `{ action, targetSocketId?, ... }` |
| `raise-hand` | client→server | `{ roomId, raised }` |
| `hand-raised` | server→room | `{ socketId, userName, raised }` |

