### Backend – Signaling Gateway

#### [MODIFY] [events.gateway.ts](file:///d:/Documents/Practice/AntiGravity/Meetify/backend/src/signaling/events.gateway.ts)

Major changes:
1. Add `pendingRequests` Map and `roomSettings` Map alongside existing `rooms` Map
2. Modify [handleJoinRoom](file:///d:/Documents/Practice/AntiGravity/Meetify/backend/src/signaling/events.gateway.ts#241-311) to check lobby settings — if enabled and not host, emit `lobby-waiting` instead of admitting
3. Add `@SubscribeMessage` handlers: `join-request`, `join-request-cancel`, `approve-request`, `deny-request`, `bulk-approve`, `host-action`, `raise-hand`
4. Update [handleDisconnect](file:///d:/Documents/Practice/AntiGravity/Meetify/backend/src/signaling/events.gateway.ts#236-239) to cleanup pending requests
5. Add TTL cleanup interval in `onModuleInit`
6. Add in-memory audit log per room

